<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#svnfuwun">凉 [liáng]</a></strong><strong>2. <a href="#dpsqllgv">凉 [liàng]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="svnfuwun">凉 [liáng]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>温度低：～快。～爽。～意。～气。阴～。～丝丝。～亭。荒～。</p></li><li><p>喻灰心，失望：听到这消息，我～了半截。</p></li><li><p>中国西晋末年至北魏，各族统治者在西北地区建立的割据政权：五～（前、后、南、北、西）。</p></li></ol></dd></dl><dl><dt><a name="dpsqllgv">凉 [liàng]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>放一会儿，使温度降低：把开水～一～再喝。</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
